title: Nicole Kidman visits Walt Disney World
text:
Nicole Kidman visits Walt Disney World Nicole Kidman Chloe Rice Oscar winner Nicole Kidman strikes a pose with Mickey Mouse on Monday at the Magic Kingdom. Oscar winner Nicole Kidman strikes a pose with Mickey Mouse on Monday at the Magic Kingdom. (Chloe Rice) Hal Boedeker (the heavy favorite for “Fences”), former winner Octavia Spencer (for “Hidden Figures”), Naomi Harris (for “Moonlight”) and Michelle Williams (for “ Manchester by the Sea ”).
It is the fourth nomination for Kidman. She won the best actress award for “The Hours.” She was a nominee in that category for “Moulin Rouge!” and “Rabbit Hole.” 
She is currently starring in “Big Little Lies” on HBO. On Monday, she was a long way from that role at the Magic Kingdom.
